node.text:
Up your sandwich game with this Italian Chicken Schnitzel Sando!

INGREDIENTS
Chicken
* 	2 chicken breast, butterflied and pounded thin
* 	2 lemons, juiced 
* 	2 tbsp olive oil
* 	3 minced garlic cloves
* 	½ tsp Chilli flakes 
* 	2 bay leaves
* 	3 thyme sprigs 
* 	A few roughly torn sage leaves
* 	2 sprigs osemary
* 	Salt and pepper
* 	1 egg, beaten
* 	½ cup panko
* 	½ cup fine breadcrumbs
 
Slaw
* 	½ White cabbage 
* 	½ White onion, thinly sliced
* 	1 tbsp Honey 
* 	2 Lemons, juiced
* 	Salt and pepper to taste
 
Salsa verde
* 	30g Parsley, finely chopped
* 	1 tbsp Capers, chopped
* 	½ red onion, finely chopped
* 	½ red chilli, finely chopped
* 	½ tsp Dijon
* 	3 tbsp Red wine vinegar 
* 	2 tbsp Olive oil 
* 	1 Anchovy
 
Artichoke Aioli
* 	1 egg yolk
* 	1 garlic clove
* 	1 tsp dijon mustard
* 	Pinch salt
* 	2 artichoke hearts 
* 	1 lemon, juiced
* 	Vegetable oil - around 100ml
 
To serve
* 	Thick white bread 

#fschnitzel #foodpics #foodphotography #foodgram #foodlovers #fooddiary #foodforthought #sandwich #eeeeeats #cheesetoastie #noleftovers #foodgasm

CROQUE MONSIEUR CROISSANT LASAGNA

INGREDIENTS
* 	10 shop-bought all-butter croissants
* 	a little butter for greasing
* 	1 1/2 cups bechamel sauce
* 	2 cups grated emmental cheese
* 	10 slices wafer thin cooked ham, plus a little more for layering
* 	nutmeg, a scrape
* 	dijon mustard, 1/2 tsp per croissant

node.text:
These balls are our favourite!

CROQUE MONSIEUR MASH BALLS
INGREDIENTS
* 6 cups cold leftover mash
* 4 slices ham, chopped into small cubes
* 3 cups grated emmental
* 2 tbsp dijon mustard
* 1/4 cup finely chopped parsley
* 1 tbsp salt
* 1 tbsp pepper
* 1 cup flour
* 4 eggs, beaten with a little milk
* 2 cups panko breadcrumbs
* Enough groundnut oil to deep fry

node.text:
Up your sandwich game with this Italian Chicken Schnitzel Sando!

INGREDIENTS
Chicken
* 	2 chicken breast, butterflied and pounded thin
* 	2 lemons, juiced 
* 	2 tbsp olive oil
* 	3 minced garlic cloves
* 	½ tsp Chilli flakes 
* 	2 bay leaves
* 	3 thyme sprigs 
* 	A few roughly torn sage leaves
* 	2 sprigs osemary
* 	Salt and pepper
* 	1 egg, beaten
* 	½ cup panko
* 	½ cup fine breadcrumbs
 
Slaw
* 	½ White cabbage 
* 	½ White onion, thinly sliced
* 	1 tbsp Honey 
* 	2 Lemons, juiced
* 	Salt and pepper to taste
 
Salsa verde
* 	30g Parsley, finely chopped
* 	1 tbsp Capers, chopped
* 	½ red onion, finely chopped
* 	½ red chilli, finely chopped
* 	½ tsp Dijon
* 	3 tbsp Red wine vinegar 
* 	2 tbsp Olive oil 
* 	1 Anchovy
 
Artichoke Aioli
* 	1 egg yolk
* 	1 garlic clove
* 	1 tsp dijon mustard
* 	Pinch salt
* 	2 artichoke hearts 
* 	1 lemon, juiced
* 	Vegetable oil - around 100ml
 
To serve
* 	Thick white bread 

#fschnitzel #foodpics #foodphotography #foodgram #foodlovers #fooddiary #foodforthought #sandwich #eeeeeats #cheesetoastie #noleftovers #foodgasm

Good news Gravy lovers - Gravy season is back! 

Cheesy beef loaded fries
Ingredients
* 1 tbsp oil
* 2.2 lb sirloin steak, cut into thin strips
* 3 tbsp flour
* 1 tbsp salt
* 1 tbsp pepper
* 1 onion, sliced roughly
* 1 tbsp tomato puree
* 2 cups beef stock
* 1 cup wine
* Thyme

HOT ROAST CHICKEN GRAVY BUNS
INGREDIENTS
* 	1 small chicken
* 	1/2 lemon
* 	1/2 bulb garlic
* 	1 1/2 tsps salt
* 	1 cup mayonnaise
* 	toasted buns, to serve
* 	1 cup chicken stock
* 	fries, to serve
* 	1 glass white wine
* 	1 tbsp french mustard
* 	1 hpd tsp plain flour

GRAVY AND MASH BOMBS
INGREDIENTS
* 	1 cup/250ml gravy
* 	3 cups/1 kilo pork mince
* 	1 tbsp chopped chives
* 	2 tbsp chopped parsley
* 	1 tbsp salt
* 	1 tsp pepper
* 	1 tsp nutmeg
* 	2 cups mashed potato
* 	1 cup plain flour
* 	4 eggs, beaten with a little milk
* 	2 cups panko breadcrumbs
* 	Groundnut oil for deep frying

Cheese stuffed mash beef Pie

* 2 1/4 lb Stewing beef
* 2 cloves Garlic
* 2 Onions
* 1 1/2 cups Beef stock
* 3 tbsp Flour
* 2 tsp Pepper
* 2 tsp Salt
* 1 tbsp Vegetable oil
* 1 tbsp Butter
* 1 small block Cheddar
* 2 cups Red wine
* 3 cups Leftover mash
* 1 tbsp Passasta
